Chris and Janique are madly in love. Made for each other. They also dominate the adult film industry with iron hands and velvet gloves, developing the future of porn tech, and trying to rule the world...

Four short stories from the forthcoming Ultimate Hustle novels Ultimate Hustle, Superlove, and Star Hustle. The collection serves as an introduction to the series, with a glimpse at where the books are headed. The innocent reader is also introduced to the twisted world of President Gorlax and High-C from the Perfect Me universe.
